<p>How do we know *which one* of the drives is going bad? They are physically identical. How do we know which is sdb2?</p>

		<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-38821' data-commentid="38821" data-postid="3317" data-belowelement="div-comment-38821" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Ferry Toth" aria-label='Reply to Ferry Toth'>Reply</a></div>
